text: Frunze () is a rural locality (a selo) in Verkhnetroitsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 241 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Tuymazy, 5 km from Verkhnetroitskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Frunze, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
